On July 4th, the park will be closing early at 12pm in observance of the Independence Day holiday, and most importantly in order to help keep our dogs safe.

The park will be open Tuesday, July 4th from 8am-12pm

This is a decision made by the team so that your dogs can get the very necessary mental and physical exercise that they will need, ahead of what can be the most terrifying night of the year for most pets. 

*CBD Treats are 40% off from today until we close on the 4th. In-store only.
